column5: Hello all look i want ta tell ya that the quinte ice is a no go,ive cancelled all hut rentals and guides for this week untill teusday next week and even thats depending on the wheather.  where were fishing we have 10" of ice but there are drain holes out there the size of my truck tires,no need to push your luck,fishing is only gonna get better,stay home and stay safe......  Hawg Hunter
Sorry folks never noticed the other warning posted  my bag lol  HAWG HUNTER
